@startuml
!theme plain
title Sample PlantUML State Diagram

[*] --> Idle
Idle : User waiting for input
Idle --> Processing : user_input
Processing : System processing data
Processing --> Success : process_complete
Processing --> Error : error_occurred
Success --> Idle : reset
Error --> Idle : retry
Success --> [*] : exit
Error --> [*] : exit

@enduml